                </listAnnotation>
                <listAnnotation xml:lang="en" type="notes">
                    
                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            

<p>Van Gogh had bought this mirror in September 1888 in Arles in order to paint self-portraits (<ref xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" target="let681.xml">see letter 681</ref>).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p>For this visit to Arles, <ref xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" target="let857.xml#n-1">see letter 857, n. 1.</ref></p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="3" xml:id="note-t-3">
                            

<p>Van Gogh is mistaken about the number: the address of Boussod, Valadon &amp; Cie was 19 boulevard Montmartre.</p>
